CloudMonitor

by James Smith (jws7) at St Andrews

Current hardware-based solutions to providing energy usage statistics are unsuitable in warehouse scale data centers where low cost and scalability are desirable properties.

CloudMonitor is a software utility that is capable of >95% accurate power predictions from monitoring resource consumption of workloads, after a "training phase" in which a dynamic power model is developed.

Written in Java

Uses SIGAR Library

GNU License
